### List all loans
GET {{host}}/api/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Loan a manga
POST {{host}}/api/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "volume_id": 1,
    "borrower_name": "Jean Dupont",
    "notes": "Prêté pour 2 semaines"
}

### Return a manga
POST {{host}}/api/loans/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "volume_id": 1
}
